0adfda00-716f-484f-a646-de1b15196dc5.title: Party Pete
0adfda00-716f-484f-a646-de1b15196dc5.text:
Hi! I'm Party Pete.
Welcome to the Party Room!

options.text: What's the big lever over there for?

229e2cd0-a113-4a79-a0ce-7dda5ad2190c.title: Party Pete
229e2cd0-a113-4a79-a0ce-7dda5ad2190c.text: This room is for partying the night away!

dc904658-c926-45e1-9c37-6c0e9d8f009a.title: <player>
dc904658-c926-45e1-9c37-6c0e9d8f009a.text: How do you have a party in Gielinor?

43793da1-8c96-4d83-938c-11bb18543d68.title: Party Pete
43793da1-8c96-4d83-938c-11bb18543d68.text: Get a few mates round, get the beers in and have fun!

621a18e5-8b54-44a1-ab49-a74f956f41e6.title: Party Pete
621a18e5-8b54-44a1-ab49-a74f956f41e6.text: Some players organise parties so keep an eye open!

df0f1382-c291-49ff-869f-7d6832153ea6.title: <player>
df0f1382-c291-49ff-869f-7d6832153ea6.text: What's the big lever over there for?

51586321-ad4d-40be-bbc1-53e7337d9837.title: Party Pete
51586321-ad4d-40be-bbc1-53e7337d9837.text: Simple. With the lever you can do some fun stuff.

6895a96f-8fea-48c8-a08d-87e2d66380f9.title: Party Pete
6895a96f-8fea-48c8-a08d-87e2d66380f9.text:
A balloon drop costs 1000 gold. For this you get 200
balloons dropped across the whole of the party room.
You can then have fun popping the balloons! If there
are items in the Party Drop Chest they will be inside

19c5dcd7-40d6-4c9b-9649-2141d3755d9d.title: Party Pete
19c5dcd7-40d6-4c9b-9649-2141d3755d9d.text:
the balloons! For 500 gold you can summon the Party
Room Knights who will dance for your delight.

6268ed38-43d8-4da9-9665-73dfa2aaa1ca.title: Party Pete
6268ed38-43d8-4da9-9665-73dfa2aaa1ca.text: Their singing isn't a delight though!

8a4c0a0c-19bd-458d-8c04-e8b1ad457c35.title: Party Pete
8a4c0a0c-19bd-458d-8c04-e8b1ad457c35.text:
Any items that are in the chest will be dropped inside
the balloons when you pull the lever!

7aa4c498-3c11-4ffd-9665-1fc484ab77fc.title: <player>
7aa4c498-3c11-4ffd-9665-1fc484ab77fc.text: Cool! Sounds like a fun way to do a drop party!

b1fda2c9-2723-4236-b0c8-7ae189f1accf.title: Party Pete
b1fda2c9-2723-4236-b0c8-7ae189f1accf.text:
A word of warning though. Any items that you put into
the chest can't be taken out again and it costs 1000
gold pieces for each balloon drop.

68f5d0b9-bae2-40ff-abc2-041f4206ef80.title: Party Pete
68f5d0b9-bae2-40ff-abc2-041f4206ef80.text:
I've won the Dance Trophy at the Kandarin Ball three
years in a trot!

27a84442-a1d3-4dfd-be8b-b62dc14df670.title: Note
27a84442-a1d3-4dfd-be8b-b62dc14df670.text: Party Pete then does the dance, clap, dance, cheer, dance then bow emotes
